OL,3,CMum says child 'could have been
OL,4,Cparalysed' after car spooked horse
OL,6,FA young rider has broken a disc in
OL,7,Ftheir back after falling off their
OL,8,Fhorse that was spooked by a car.
OL,10,FAtlas Prow has shared concerns for
OL,11,Ftheir safety and others following the
OL,12,Fincident in Castel, Guernsey on
OL,13,FThursday 29 August at approximately
OL,14,F3pm.
OL,16,FAtlas says a passing car scared the
OL,17,Fanimal and it started to gallop before
OL,18,Fthrowing them off into a wall.
