OL,3,CMum says child 'could have been
OL,4,Cparalysed' after car spooked horse
OL,6,FThe island is known for having some
OL,7,Fnarrow roads but Atlas wants motorists
OL,8,Fto be more aware of the risks and
OL,9,Fdistances when driving around horses.
OL,11,FThey said: "My lower back ended up
OL,12,Fhitting a small wall and I was
OL,13,Fscreaming.
OL,15,F"There was a woman that saw me and
OL,16,Fcalled the ambulance, my mum came as
OL,17,Fwell"
OL,19,F"Usually I can calm him down (Rupert
OL,20,Fthe horse) but he was already
OL,21,Firritated."
