OL,3,CMum says child 'could have been
OL,4,Cparalysed' after car spooked horse
OL,6,FTheir mother Julie Prow wants road
OL,7,Fusers to be more considerate of each
OL,8,Fother.
OL,10,FShe explains: "I am surpised they
OL,11,Fstayed on as long as they did, it's
OL,12,Ffrightening. After hitting the wall,
OL,13,Fthey could have been paralysed.
OL,15,F"You know, that there's a possibility
OL,16,Fthat when they fall off, they might
OL,17,Fnot be able to get back up.
OL,19,F"It could have been a massive traffic
OL,20,Faccident, I don't want it to happen to
OL,21,Fanyone else."
