OL,6,FGuernsey Police are investigating the
OL,7,Fincident which happened along Vazon
OL,8,FRoad, near to Richmond Kiosk.
OL,10,FOfficers would like to speak to the
OL,11,Fdriver of the vehicle involved and
OL,12,Fanyone who may have information, CCTV
OL,13,For dashcam footage.
OL,15,FWitnesses are asked to call PC 28 Matt
OL,16,FShields on 01481 222222 or
OL,17,FCrimestoppers anonymously on 0800
OL,18,F555111.
